        "created_at": "2021-10-23T09:40:36.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The For\u00eats is the richest and most complete wine (which makes sense given the size and location of the parcel). Clos de l\u2019Arlot is the most ethereal. The Suchots is a touch broader-shouldered than the Clos de l\u2019Arlot, but not as concentrated as the For\u00eats nor as complete. Maybe the vine genetics are not as optimal.</p>",
